import React from 'react'
import Chart from '../Chart/Chart'

const ExpensesChart = ({ expenses }) => { 
    const chartPoints = [
        { label: 'Jan', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Feb', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Mar', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Apr', value: 0 },
        { label: 'May', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Jun', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Jul', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Aug', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Sep', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Oct', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Nov', value: 0 },
        { label: 'Dec', value: 0 },
    ]
    for (const expense of expenses) { 
        const month = expense.date.get
       chartPoints[expense].value = expense.price 
    }

    return (
        <Chart dataPoints={ chartPoints } />
    )
}
export default ExpensesChart
